{"tid":1208621,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[舊聞回帶]英國倫敦蓋特威克機場（Gatwick Airport）多次受無人機影響關閉超過一天","createTime":"2019-06-12T09:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T01:46:46.000Z","uid":259294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fa8cf0378fde99ecdf7daafad7e218d142572c2","tid":1208621,"uid":259294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 與其玩地鐵 不如大家一齊睇下半年前既一則國際新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-46651290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-46651290&d=LMVY6Z7nIekaHefcscWgVZLurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=f9dce1a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fscience-46651290&h=bd1952b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/science-46651290</a><br />\n<br />\n英國倫敦蓋特威克機場（Gatwick Airport）多次受無人機影響關閉超過一天，影響超過700架次航班升降，約十萬名旅客受影響。當地警方至今仍然未找到操作無人機的人，但懷疑可能是環保份子所為。<br />\n<br />\n蓋特威克機場發言人指，英國警方和軍隊已經為機場提供額外的防範措施，讓機場可以重新開放，讓飛機升降。<br />\n<br />\n現今許多無人機售價廉宜，低至數十美元就可以買到。但BBC科技事務記者珍‧韋克菲爾德（Jane Wakefield）的報道指，這些小小的航空器可以對民航交通造成巨大影響。"},{"pid":"5b95f50afcd45312ef240fd2138c47250a4b2b60","tid":1208621,"uid":61494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420596644bcd20880985089d6e3bc6ffc24adf77","tid":1208621,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:46:46.000Z","msg":"香港易被人捉好多<br />\n<br />\n英國格域 四周都係路"}]}